PART 1: T-3 Taxonomic Misplacement (3 samples)
Generate Arabic scholarly excerpts where a concept exists in MULTIPLE Islamic sciences, and the text discusses it in one science but uses terminology common to another. A naive keyword-based classifier would place it in the WRONG science.

